---
import Heart from "@/icons/heart.astro";
import Layers from "@/icons/layers.astro";
import Mail from "@/icons/mail.astro";
import User from "@/icons/user.astro";
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="About - Abhin Rustagi"
  description="Full-stack developer with a passion for building thoughtful web experiences."
>
  <section>
    <div class="container section-wrapper border-dashed-b">
      <h1 class="section-title">
        <User size={20} class="section-title-icon" />About
      </h1>
      <div class="bio animate-in animate-in-delay-1 text-muted">
        <p>
          Hi, my name is Abhin, a software engineer who loves a good challenge.
          In the past, I've had the opportunity to develop software across a
          variety of settings â€” from an innovative EdTech platform, or a
          creative MedTech solution, to just as a freelance agent for startups
          trying to find their feet making it big. Additionally, I also
          volunteer my time and engineering skills to help organisations fight
          the climate change battle.
        </p>
        <p>
          Dreaming up cool automative yet productivity and user-first ideas and
          making them come true is where my passion lies. I started programming
          in 2017, and made it my career in 2021. My roles have spanned the
          entire stack, from frontend to backend, and from AI to DevOps, and I
          have enjoyed almost every minute of it.
        </p>
        <p>
          In my spare time, I'm usually at the gym, climbing, enjoying cricket,
          researching new places to eat at or planning my next travel.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="skills animate-in animate-in-delay-2">
    <div class="container section-wrapper border-dashed-b">
      <h2 class="section-title">
        <Layers size={20} class="section-title-icon" />Stack
      </h2>
      <p>
        Some technologies where I've spend most of my coding hours, but not
        limited to:
        <span class="skill-list">
          React, Next.js, TypeScript, Node.js, Python, PostgreSQL, Redis,
          Tailwind CSS, Astro, Docker, AWS, Vercel
        </span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div
      class="container section-wrapper border-dashed-b animate-in animate-in-delay-3"
    >
      <h2 class="section-title">
        <Heart size={20} class="section-title-icon" />Good words
      </h2>
      <div class="testimony">
        <p class="text-muted">
          Abhin is a complete package. His communication and understanding of
          startups made collaboration smooth and efficient.
        </p>
        <p>Chris Illuk, Co-Founder Layer Licensing, Accord</p>
      </div>
      <div class="testimony">
        <p class="text-muted">
          What I appreciate most about Abhin is his commitment. He's not just
          ticking boxes and doing tasks, he wants his work to mean something, to
          make a real impact.
        </p>
        <p>Prudhvi Dharmana, Founder ReWorld Earth</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-muted">
          Abhin has flawless work ethic, he is an amazing team member, and his
          work is of the upmost quality.
        </p>
        <p>Ricardo Rosas, Founder Virtetic</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact animate-in animate-in-delay-4">
    <div class="container section-wrapper">
      <h2 class="section-title">
        <Mail size={20} class="section-title-icon" />Contact
      </h2>
      <p>
        I'm always open to interesting projects and collaborations via email at
        <span>hi[at]abhin[dot]dev</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .bio p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .bio p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .skill-list {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .contact p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .testimony {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .contact a {
    color: var(--text);
  }
</style>
